---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout 
  title="The Ministry Resource Hub" 
  description="The definitive resource for evangelism, discipleship, Ekklesia, and digital evangelism. Frameworks and tools from RK Castillo to help you finish the Great Commission."
>

<style>
  .hero {
    background: var(--pc-navy);
    padding: 80px 24px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, #1170C320 0%, transparent 70%);
  }
  .hero-inner { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; position: relative; }
  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--pc-blue-light);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 7vw, 72px);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: white;
    line-height: 1.05;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .hero h1 em {
    color: var(--pc-blue-electric);
    font-style: normal;
    display: block;
  }
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--pc-gray-light);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto 36px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .hero-cta { display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }

  /* CATEGORIES */
  .categories {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 72px 24px;
  }
  .section-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--pc-blue);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--pc-navy);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .cat-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .cat-card {
    background: var(--pc-navy);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 32px 28px;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid #1170C330;
    transition: all 0.25s;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .cat-card::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--pc-blue);
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transition: transform 0.25s;
  }
  .cat-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); border-color: var(--pc-blue); }
  .cat-card:hover::after { transform: scaleX(1); }
  .cat-number {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #1170C320;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .cat-card h2 {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: white;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .cat-card p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #aaa;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .cat-link {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: var(--pc-blue-light);
  }

  /* MISSION STRIP */
  .mission-strip {
    background: var(--pc-blue);
    padding: 48px 24px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .mission-strip p {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(22px, 4vw, 36px);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: white;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .mission-strip p em {
    color: var(--pc-blue-electric);
    font-style: normal;
  }

  /* ABOUT */
  .about {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 72px 24px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .about-text h2 {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--pc-navy);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .about-text p {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--pc-gray-dark);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .about-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .stat-card {
    background: var(--pc-navy);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 24px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .stat-number {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 40px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--pc-blue-electric);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #aaa;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .about-stats { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }
</style>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <p class="hero-eyebrow">Purpose Concepts Resource Hub</p>
    <h1>Reach Everyone.<em>Disciple All The Nations.</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">The definitive resource library for evangelism, discipleship, Ekklesia, and digital evangelism — built on the frameworks of RK Castillo.</p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a href="/evangelism" class="btn-green">Start With Evangelism</a>
      <a href="https://purposeconcepts.com" class="btn-blue">Join The Newsletter</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- MISSION STRIP -->
<div class="mission-strip">
  <p>The goal: <em>the all and the every</em> — reach every person and disciple all the nations.</p>
</div>

<!-- CATEGORIES -->
<section class="categories">
  <p class="section-label">Browse By Category</p>
  <h2 class="section-title">Four Pillars of the Great Commission</h2>
  <div class="cat-grid">
    <a href="/evangelism" class="cat-card">
      <div class="cat-number">01</div>
      <h2>Evangelism</h2>
      <p>How to preach the Gospel, heal the sick, cast out demons, hear God's voice, and start conversations about Jesus anywhere.</p>
      <span class="cat-link">Explore Evangelism →</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/discipleship" class="cat-card">
      <div class="cat-number">02</div>
      <h2>Discipleship</h2>
      <p>What it means to disciple nations — not just individuals. DMM, Discovery Bible Studies, and the Worker Maker framework.</p>
      <span class="cat-link">Explore Discipleship →</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/ekklesia" class="cat-card">
      <div class="cat-number">03</div>
      <h2>Ekklesia</h2>
      <p>The Proverbs 31 Ekklesia, church planting movements, CPM, and what it means to gather as the called-out community of the King.</p>
      <span class="cat-link">Explore Ekklesia →</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/digital-evangelism" class="cat-card">
      <div class="cat-number">04</div>
      <h2>Digital Evangelism</h2>
      <p>The O2F Method. Facebook ads that get new church visitors every Sunday. How to use social media to do evangelism, discipleship, and church planting.</p>
      <span class="cat-link">Explore Digital Evangelism →</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section class="about">
  <div class="about-text">
    <h2>About This Hub</h2>
    <p>This is the resource library for Purpose Concepts — the home of RK Castillo's frameworks for finishing the Great Commission. Every article is rooted in years of field-tested ministry across six continents.</p>
    <p>From stadium evangelism to street outreach, from homeless churches in Waikiki to missionary training in Paraguay, these frameworks come from doing — not just theorizing.</p>
    <a href="https://workermaker.com" class="btn-green" style="display:inline-block;margin-top:8px;">Join the Worker Maker Community</a>
  </div>
  <div class="about-stats">
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-number">6</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Continents of ministry</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-number">25+</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Years in missions</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-number">1K+</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Prayer requests in 4 days</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-number">$0.18</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Cost per church visitor</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
